--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- @jrc03c/email/standardize-email-adddress/tests
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- target : https://www.guidedtrack.com/programs/34794/edit
-- author : Josh Castle (joshrcastle@gmail.com)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

>> error_is_fatal = "no"

*html
	<h1 style="color: black;">
		All of these tests should pass:
	</h1>

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

>> email_address = "someone"
>> should_convert_domain_to_punycode = 0
>> should_remove_diacritical_marks_in_username = 1
>> should_remove_periods_in_username = 0
>> should_remove_tags_in_username = 0

*program: @jrc03c/email/standardize-email-address

*if: email_address_standardized = "someone"
	>> success_message = "'{email_address_standardized}' = 'someone'"
	*program: @jrc03c/show-success

*if: not (email_address_standardized = "someone")
	>> error_message = "'{email_address_standardized}' != 'someone'"
	*program: @jrc03c/show-error

*wait: 1.seconds

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

